oogle-ai-future-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20DeepMind%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0created%20the%20model%2C%20and%20it's%20integrating%20it%20into%20the%20Gemini%20app%20and%20website%20so%20that%20anyone%20can%20use%20it.%20While%20it%20was%20tested%20under%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BNano%20Banana%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20model%20is%20actually%20named%20Gemini%202.5%20Flash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20been%20testing%20the%20new%20model%20on%20LMArena%2C%20a%20public%20site%20that%20crowdsources%20anonymous%20feedback%20on%20AI%20model%20quality.%20It%20showed%20up%20as%20Nano%20Banana%2C%20but%20users%20were%20quick%20to%20guess%20that%20Google%20was%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20said%20Gemini%202.5%20Flash's%20particular%20strength%20is%20in%20keeping%20a%20person%20or%20animal's%20likeness%20the%20same%20from%20image%20to%20image.%20Based%20on%20the%20feedback%20so%20far%2C%20Google%20claims%20that%20users%20prefer%20the%20new%20model%20over%20those%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20other%20rivals%2C%20based%20on%20its%20Elo%20score%20%E2%80%94%20a%20method%20for%20calculating%20the%20relative%20skill%20levels%20of%20generative%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20been%20testing%20the%20model%20for%20several%20days%2C%20and%20we've%20found%20it%20generally%20better%20than%20rival%20tools.%20It's%20not%20perfect%20%E2%80%94%20it%20sometimes%20struggled%20to%20replicate%20faces%20when%20combining%20two%20different%20photos%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20especially%20strong%20at%20making%20small%20tweaks%20to%20existing%20pictures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20example%20below%2C%20we%20asked%20it%20to%20add%20glasses%20to%20the%20photo%20of%20this%20article's%20author%20and%20to%20change%20the%20color%20of%20the%20T-shirt%20to%20red.%20While%20several%20models%20got%20the%20glasses%20and%20the%20color%20correct%2C%20Google's%20was%20the%20only%20one%20to%20retain%20the%20stripe%20pattern%20on%20the%20T-shirt.%20It%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20sharp