%20of%20your%20cup.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd3b12eb-c11e-4624-8a01-8d03364c28ca%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20order%20a%20drink%20'%3Cu%3Eskinny%3C%2Fu%3E%2C'%20the%20barista%20will%20use%20sugar-free%20syrup%20and%20nonfat%20milk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSkinny%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20in%20a%20skinny%20vanilla%20latte%2C%20refers%20to%20substituting%20the%20appropriate%20syrup%20and%20milk%20with%20sugar-free%20and%20nonfat%2C%20respectively.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20popular%20trick%20for%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20calories%20in%20an%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20only%20be%20fully%20applied%20to%20drinks%20that%20have%20syrups%20that%20come%20in%20sugar-free%20varieties%2C%20such%20as%20vanilla%2C%20caramel%2C%20and%20mocha.%20Other%20drinks%20without%20alternative%20syrup%20options%20would%20just%20be%20made%20with%20nonfat%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de621fd8-4b71-46e8-bbc1-b0584d5643c7%5C%22%3EThe%20'%3Cu%3ELte%3C%2Fu%3E'%20on%20your%20cup%20can%20apply%20to%20ice%2C%20syrup%2C%20and%20other%20add-ons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22macchiato%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58b86ac2b09d1327008b462a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223165%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20order%20your%20Starbucks%20drink%20with%20light%20ice%2C%20light%20foam%2C%20or%20light%20whip.%3Cp%3EChira%20Jangjan%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BLte%26quot%3B%20written%20on%20your%20Starbucks%20cup%20refers%20to%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Blight.%26quot%3B%20It%20means%20there's%20a%20bit%20less%20than%20usual%20of%20whatever's%20written%20after%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20%26quot%3BLte%20ice%26quot%3B%20means%20you%20asked%20for%20less%20ice%20in%20your%20drink.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20term%20could%20apply%20to%20any%20addition%20to%20a%20drink%2C%20such%20as%20ice%2C%20syrup%2C%20foam%2C%20or%20whipped%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283523ae2-9123-48be-9797-81372e5d6997%5C%22%3EMany%20coffee%20shops%20serve%20a%20%3Cu%3Emacchiato%3C%2Fu%3E%20and%20at%20Starbucks%2C%20you%20can%20combine%20it%20with%20a%20latte%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20popular%20coffee%20drink%2C%20macchiatos%20consist%20of%20espresso%20shots%20poured%20over%20a%20bit%20of%20foamy%20milk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-items-at-starbucks-employees-favorites-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epopular%20macchiatos%20at%20Starbucks%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20caramel%20one%2C%20but%20you%20can%20actually%20turn%20a%20plain%20latte%20into%20a%20macchiato%20just%20by%20ordering%20a%20%26quot%3Blatte%20macchiato.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20latte%20macchiato%2C%20the%20espresso%20is%20closer%20to%20the%20top%20of%20your%20beverage%2C%20which%20can%20give%20your%20drink%20a%20bolder%20flavor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dda7bbde-b4bc-4fd1-b006-55077ffdf0f9%5C%22%3EAt%20Starbucks%2C%20you%20can%20order%20an%20%3Cu%3Eaffogato-style%3C%2Fu%3E%20Frappuccino%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20affogato%20is%20an%20Italian%20treat%20that%20consists%20of%20a%20hot%20espresso%20shot%20served%20over%20cold%20gelato%20or%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Starbucks%2C%20you%20can%20order%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoolest-starbucks-frappuccinos-world-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffogato-style%20Frappuccino%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20means%20you'll%20get%20a%20shot%20of%20espresso%20poured%20over%20your%20Frapp.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20costs%20a%20little%20bit%20extra%20and%20can%20be%20done%20to%20just%20about%20any%20Frappuccino%2C%20but%20check%20with%20your%20barista%20as%20this%20customization%20option%20may%20not%20be%20available%20at%20every%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4897197-8476-4e6e-a7df-aa9cffe74a1c%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERistretto%3C%2Fu%3E%20and%20%3Cu%3Elong-shot%3C%2Fu%3E%20are%20two%20different%20types%20of%20espresso%20shots%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223808%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22iced%20starbucks%20drink%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ef25438f34d052fef668f65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222856%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20iced%20latte%20can%20be%20ordered%20with%20different%20types%20of%20espresso%20shots.%3Cp%3EZhang%20Peng%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20many%20coffee%20shops%2C%20at%20Starbucks%2C%20there's%20more%20than%20one%20kind%20of%20espresso%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20shot%20that's%20ristretto%2C%20which%20is%20Italian%20for%20%26quot%3Brestricted%2C%26quot%3B%20uses%20less%20hot%20water%20when%20brewing%20the%20espresso%20to%20get%20a%20more%20concentrated%20flavor.%20This%20results%20in%20a%20stronger%20and%20smoother%20shot.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20long-shot%20is%20the%20opposite%2C%20and%20it%20uses%20more%20hot%20water%20than%20is%20standard%20when%20brewing%20espresso.%20This%20creates%20an%20espresso%20shot%20with%20a%20milder%20taste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22134d02da-f720-4d82-8d4c-164397a5742f%5C%22%3EA%20%3Cu%3Ered-eye%3C%2Fu%3E%20is%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%20with%20one%20espresso%20shot%2C%20and%20a%20%3Cu%3Eblack-eye%3C%2Fu%3E%20is%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%20with%20two%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERed-eye%20is%20a%20term%20used%20for%20a%20shot%20of%20espresso%20in%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee.%20This%20is%20a%20popular%20choice%20among%20the%20morning%20crowd%20who%20want%20an%20extra%20bit%20of%20caffeine%20to%20get%20them%20through%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20add%20another%20shot%20of%20espresso%20to%20the%20coffee%2C%20it's%20a%20black-eye.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20your%20drink%20won't%20be%20labeled%20in%20our%20system%20as%20red-eye%20or%20black-eye%2C