ng%20things%20about%20visiting%20Atlantic%20City%20was%20the%20access%20to%20the%20Jersey%20Shore%20beach.%20This%20is%20one%20area%20where%20AC%20has%20a%20leg%20up%20on%20destinations%20like%20Vegas%3A%20Just%20steps%20from%20many%20of%20the%20boardwalk%20casino%20resorts%20is%20the%20beach%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20nice%20beach%20at%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20multiple%20mornings%20walking%20along%20its%20sandy%20shores%2C%20swimming%20in%20the%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20though%20admittedly%20very%20cold%20%E2%80%94%20waters%2C%20and%20lounging%20on%20the%20sand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20used%20to%20lugging%20my%20beach%20gear%20down%20winding%20trails%2C%20or%20taking%20an%20hourlong%20ferry%20or%20even%20longer%20subway%20ride%20to%20one%20of%20the%20New%20York%20City%20beaches.%20This%20was%20a%20completely%20different%20experience%2C%20since%20the%20beach%20entrance%20was%20located%20just%20off%20the%20boardwalk%20and%20unbelievably%20easy%20to%20get%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beach%20was%20also%20free%20to%20access%2C%20even%20if%20you're%20not%20staying%20at%20one%20of%20the%20boardwalk%20casinos.%20While%20most%20of%20the%20beaches%20in%20New%20York%20City%20are%20also%20free%20to%20access%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20the%20beach%20in%20Atlantic%20City%20was%20free%20given%20how%20close%20they%20were%20to%20the%20resorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20were%20other%20free%20activities%2C%20too%2C%20from%20fireworks%20shows%20to%20strolls%20on%20the%20boardwalk.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ocean%20casino%20resort%20atlantic%20city%20firework%20show%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a78d62cfc04e97619bd115%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20beach%2C%20Atlantic%20City%20offers%20other%20free%20activities%20to%20pass%20the%20tim