he%20company%20closed%20its%20seed%20round%20in%20June%202024%20and%20started%20building%20last%20August%2C%20said%20Aurasell%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Jason%20Eubanks%2C%20who%20briefly%20worked%20as%20a%20venture%20partner%20at%20Next47.%20Next47%20led%20the%20funding%20round%2C%20which%20also%20featured%20participation%20from%20Menlo%20Ventures%20and%20Unusual%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEubanks%20worked%20as%20a%20sales%20executive%20for%2020%20years%20at%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciscos-cpo-shares-2-most-valuable-skills-engineers-ai-era-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECisco%3C%2Fa%3E%20Meraki%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-acquisition-targets-cloud-software-zoom-twilio-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETwilio%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20cofounded%20Aurasell%20with%20CTO%20Srinivas%20Bandi%2C%20with%20whom%20he%20previously%20worked%20at%20software%20delivery%20company%20Harness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20bloat%20is%20not%20only%20costly%20but%20a%20productivity%20killer%20for%20sales%20teams%2C%20Eubanks%20said.%20He%20said%20that%20when%20he%20worked%20at%20Harness%2C%20the%20company%20had%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20different%20tools%20supporting%20sales%20teams%20and%20spent%20millions%20annually%20on%20software%20subscription%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20an%20opportunity%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20inject%20intelligence%20in%20an%20automated%20way%20into%20these%20processes%20that%20were%20formally%20manual%2C%26quot%3B%20Eubanks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEubanks%20said%20Aurasell%20raised%20the%20first%20%2425%20million%20in%2012%20hours%2C%20and%20the%20round%20was%20initially%20oversubscribed%20at%20%2440%20million%20before%20it%20was%20walked%20back%20down.%20Aurasell's%20investors%20had%20been%20on%20the%20boards%20of%20companies%20where%20he%20and%20Bandi%20had%20previously%20worked%2C%20and%20they%20were%20drawn%20by%20the%20lucrative%20problem%20A