20surfaces%20and%20fewer%20permeable%20zones%2C%20the%20cityscape%20now%20prevents%20natural%20rainwater%20absorption%2C%20leading%20to%20surface%20runoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMunicipal%20Commissioner%20Gaurav%20Singh%20Sogarwal%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20drainage%20was%20built%20for%20a%20smaller%20and%20less%20developed%20city.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20monsoons%20dump%20volumes%20it%20was%20never%20meant%20to%20handle.%E2%80%9D%20The%20ageing%20drains%20often%20fail%2C%20especially%20when%20blocked%20by%20waste%20or%20silt%2C%20causing%20backflow%20into%20residential%20areas%20and%20prolonged%20water%20stagnation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20is%20severe%20%E2%80%94%20stagnant%20floodwaters%20disrupt%20daily%20life%20for%20days%2C%20damage%20homes%2C%20and%20create%20ideal%20conditions%20for%20the%20spread%20of%20waterborne%20diseases%20such%20as%20dengue%20and%20cholera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20turning%20point%3A%20Launching%20the%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20Centre%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202023%2C%20the%20Gorakhpur%20Municipal%20Corporation%20partnered%20with%20Canarys%20Automations%20to%20tackle%20this%20systemic%20challenge%20head-on.%20Together%2C%20they%20designed%20and%20implemented%20the%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20brings%20processes%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20people%20together%20to%20manage%20urban%20flooding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120149.319_11zon-1754980329.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20Centre%20guides%20pump%20operations%2C%20monitors%20water%20levels%20constantly%2C%20and%20deploys%20teams%20precisely%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F