y%20control%20room%2C%20supporting%20real-time%20decision-making%20both%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20We%20do%20not%20just%20deliver%20software%2C%20we%20stay%20involved%20throughout%20%E2%80%93%20before%2C%20during%2C%20and%20after%20each%20rain%20event.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushparaj%20Shetty%2C%20Director%20and%20Business%20Head%20at%20Canarys%20Telemetry%20Department%2C%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20guide%20pump%20operations%2C%20monitor%20water%20levels%20constantly%2C%20and%20deploy%20teams%20precisely.%20This%20active%20involvement%20has%20changed%20Gorakhpur%E2%80%99s%20response%20from%20chaos%20to%20coordination.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilt%20with%20the%20community%2C%20for%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20defining%20feature%20of%20the%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%20is%20the%20citizen-facing%20%E2%80%98Varuna%E2%80%99%20app%2C%20which%20will%20allow%20residents%20to%20receive%20flood%20alerts%20and%20report%20issues%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20residents%20like%20Ratna%2C%20the%20helpline%20number%20altered%20her%20sense%20of%20helplessness.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20if%20I%20see%20blocked%20drains%20or%20rising%20water%2C%20I%20report%20it%20immediately%2C%20and%20municipal%20teams%20respond%20quickly.%20I%20finally%20feel%20at%20peace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Canarys%20Automations%20sends%20its%20field%20engineers%20directly%20to%20waterlogged%20areas%20and%20known%20hotspots%20during%20rain%20events%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120614.344_11zon-1754980588-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485271%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECanarys%20Automations%20sends%20its%20field%20engineers%20directly%20to%20waterlogged%20areas%20and%20known%20hotspots%20during%20rain%20events%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushparaj%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20soon%20launching%20our%20citizen-facing%20%E2%80%98Varuna%E2%80%99%20app%2C%20which%20will%20change%20citizens%20into%20frontline%20observers%20and%20responders.%20This%20will%20further%20strengthen%20trust%20and%20accelerate%20response.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Sanitary%20Inspector%20DK%20Bironiya%20supports%20this%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20receive%20instant%20notifications%20from%20the%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20Centre%20(UFMC)%20through%20WhatsApp%20messages%20or%20walkie-talkie-based%20transmissions%20whenever%20residents%20report%20complaints%20or%20waterlogging.%20This%20direct%20flow%20of%20information%20helps%20us%20to%20respond%20more%20quickly%20and%20efficiently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20dedicated%20grievance%20portal%2C%20community%20involvement%20has%20become%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20flood%20preparedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIntelligence%20at%20the%20core%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Early%20Warning%20System%20(EWS)%20plus%20Decision%20Support%20System%20(DSS)%20fuses%20multiple%20data%20sources%20%E2%80%94%20including%20weather%20forecasts%2C%20live%20rainfall%20data%2C%20water%20level%20sensor%20readings%2C%20drainage%20flow%20measurements%2C%20and%20historical%20flood%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%20the%20EWS%20enables%20accurate%20rainfall%20forecasting%20and%20live%20water-level%20monitoring%2C%20supporting%20early%20pump%20activation%20and%20field%20deployment.%20In%20the%20long%20term%2C%20the%20DSS%20helps%20analyse%20structural%20weaknesses%20and%20identify%20priority%20zones%20for%20drainage%20improvement%2C%20flood%20barriers%2C%20and%20urban%20redesign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheshadri%20summarises%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20DSS%20acts%20as%20a%20strategic%20engine%3B%20it%20offers%20insight%20not%20just%20for%20managing%20floods%20but%20for%20rebuilding%20city%20infrastructure%20intelligently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Early%20Warning%20System%20(EWS)%20plus%20Decision%20Support%20System%20(DSS)%20fuses%20multiple%20data%20sources%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T120908.426_11zon-1754980764-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485278%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Early%20Warning%20System%20(EWS)%20plus%20Decision%20Support%20System%20(DSS)%20fuses%20multiple%20data%20sources%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20prediction%20to%20protection%3A%20A%20fully%20coordinated%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20system%20operates%20through%20three%20interconnected%20stages%3A%20Predict%2C%20Prepare%2C%20and%20Protect.%20Each%20stage%20is%20operationalised%20through%20dedicated%20SoPs%20(Standard%20Operating%20Procedures).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3EPrediction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20system%20integrates%20rainfall%20forecasts%20from%20an%20AI-based%20forecasting%20model%20tailored%20to%20Gorakhpur.%20These%20rainfall%20forecasts%20are%20then%20used%20to%20forecast%20the%20waterlogging%20locations%20in%20the%20city.%20Forecasts%20are%20delivered%20at%20ward-level%20resolution%2C%20helping%20anticipate%20rainfall%20and%20flood%20zones%20up%20to%2024%20hours%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrepare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20hinges%20on%20these%20predictions.%20Municipal%20teams%20conduct%20pre-rain%20drain%20clean-up%20operations%2C%20schedule%20pump%20maintenance%2C%20and%20pre-position%20mobile%20pumps%20and%20suction%20machines.%20A%20day%20before%20forecasted%20rainfall%2C%20officials%20receive%20detailed%20preparedness%20reports%20while%20UFMC%C2%A0%20broadcasts%20alerts%20and%20instructions%20to%20the%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushparaj%20emphasises%20the%20difference%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20advanced%20notice%2C%20we%20deploy%20pumps%20and%20crews%20ahead%20of%20flooding.%20Instead%20of%20scrambling%20after%20streets%20are%20submerged%2C%20we%20are%20organising%20before%20the%20deluge%20arrives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3EProtect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20stage%20begins%20when%20rain%20hits.%20The%20real-time%20DSS%20tracks%20water%20levels%2C%20pump%20activity%2C%20and%20team%20movements.%20Communication%20between%20the%20control%20room%20and%20field%20teams%20flows%20continuously%20through%20walkie-talkies%20and%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20Gorakhpur%E2%80%99s%2025%20pumping%20stations%2C%2021%20have%20been%20automated%20via%20SCADA%20(Supervisory%20Control%20and%20Data%20Acquisition)%20technology.%20This%20allows%20engineers%20and%20staff%20to%20operate%20pumps%20remotely%20from%20the%20control%20room%20%E2%80%94%20significantly%20reducing%20delays%20and%20improving%20drainage%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECitizen%20grievances%20logged%20through%20the%20grievance%20portal%20feed%20directly%20into%20operational%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121340.915_11zon-1754981038.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Municipal%20teams%20conduct%20pre-rain%20drain%20clean-up%20operations%2C%20schedule%20pump%20maintenance%2C%20and%20pre-position%20mobile%20pumps%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-202