0If%20required%2C%20we%20also%20deploy%20mobile%20pumps%20to%20reinforce%20these%20efforts.%20This%20proactive%20coordination%20does%20not%20just%20save%20time%2C%20it%20prevents%20water%20from%20entering%20homes%20and%20ultimately%20helps%20protect%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrong%20leadership%20made%20it%20possible%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmbedding%20such%20a%20system%20requires%20committed%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayor%20Dr.%20Manglesh%20Kumar%20Srivastava%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%20gives%20us%20tools%20to%20anticipate%20floods%20and%20act%20proactively%2C%20not%20only%20protecting%20properties%20but%20restoring%20civic%20trust.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMunicipal%20Commissioner%20Gaurav%20Singh%20Sogarwal%20elaborates%2C%20%E2%80%9CRealigning%20city%20operations%2C%20deploying%20predictive%20systems%2C%20and%20involving%20citizens%20via%20our%20dedicated%20grievance%20portal%20represent%20institutional%20and%20cultural%20change.%20Throughout%20this%20journey%2C%20the%20team%20from%20Canarys%20has%20consistently%20supported%20us%20with%20hands-on%20collaboration%2C%20training%2C%20and%20real-time%20guidance.%20Their%20presence%20has%20been%20important%20in%20making%20this%20change%20both%20possible%20and%20sustainable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20partnership%20to%20full%20operation%3A%20A%20disciplined%20timeline%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20began%20in%202023%20to%202024%2C%20when%20Gorakhpur%E2%80%99s%20municipal%20leaders%20partnered%20with%20Canarys%20to%20shift%20from%20reactive%20flood%20response%20to%20proactive%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20in%20April%202024%2C%20the%20ideation%20phase%20was%20launched%2C%20outlining%20goals%20like%20predictive%20monitoring%2C%20process%20automation%2C%20inter-agency%20coordination%2C%20and%20citizen%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20May%20and%20August%202024%2C%20the%20design%20and%20activation%20phase%20took%20shape.%20Canarys%20brought%20in%20expertise%20in%20hydrometeorological%20modelling%2C%20real-time%20monitoring%2C%20and%20automation.%20IoT-enabled%20sensors%2C%20cloud-based%20analytics%2C%20and%20rainfall-to-response%20simulations%20were%20implemented.%20Simultaneously%2C%20the%20UFMC%20was%20established%20to%20act%20as%20a%20real-time%20operations%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20System%20was%20inaugurated%20recently%2C%20and%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20see%20more%20impact%20in%20the%20coming%20years%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-12T121641.599_11zon-1754981216-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485292%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%2