Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20I%20was%20in%20my%2050s%2C%20and%20I%20had%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20I%20really%20just%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20to%20help%20people%2C%20like%20my%20parents%20had%20always%20done%20for%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20were%20givers.%20They%20raised%20me%20with%20the%20mantra%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20whom%20much%20is%20given%2C%20much%20is%20required.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20childhood%2C%20my%20father%20often%20talked%20to%20me%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fhow-to-save-money%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20saving%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20investing.%20When%20I%20was%20volunteering%20with%20foster%20children%20during%20my%20sabbatical%2C%20it%20made%20me%20realize%20just%20how%20fortunate%20I%20was.%20I%20always%20thought%20about%20the%20children%20who%20don't%20have%20parents%20to%20talk%20to%20about%20money%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20something%20that%20could%20outlive%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221091%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shireen%20Eddleblute%20picture%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a87136a17a8c5b40534cd9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22818%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShireen%20Eddleblute%20worked%20in%20investment.%20Now%20she%20writes%20children's%20books.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Shireen%20Eddleblute%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20this%20leap%20of%20faith%20to%20finally%20focus%20on%20my%20passion%20project%2C%20which%20would%20become%20my%20second%20career%20pivot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20investing%20to%20start%20my%20company%2C%20Sprouting%20Sparks%2C%20which%20makes%20kids'%20books%20on%20financial%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20goal%20was%20to%20try%20to%20reach%20these%20kids%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20between%20the%20ages%20of%20four%20and%20eight%2C%20so%