%20The%20growth%20mindset%20that%20the%20senior%20people%20have%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20they%20can%20deal%20with%20many%20different%20situations%20and%20asset%20classes.%20This%20is%20something%20I'm%20trying%20to%20develop%2C%20but%20of%20course%2C%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20room%20to%20grow.%20As%20an%20analyst%2C%20you%20focus%20much%20more%20on%20a%20specific%20asset%20or%20a%20specific%20project%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20think%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20overall%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20fascinating%20to%20see%20PMs%20expressing%20views%20on%20different%20things%20and%20changing%20those%20views%20based%20on%20the%20circumstances.%20Being%20able%20to%20think%20quickly%20and%20do%20some%20approximation%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20not%20caring%20as%20much%20about%20having%20the%20exact%20results%20or%20exact%20price%2C%20but%20rather%20wanting%20some%20heuristic%2C%20some%20intuition.%20And%20if%20they%20see%20that%20there's%20not%20an%20opportunity%2C%20they%20don't%20keep%20obsessing%20about%20it.%20That%20deep%20humility%20it's%20something%20that%20really%20surprised%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20What%20does%20a%20normal%20day%20at%20work%20look%20like%20for%20you%3F%20What%20does%20the%20day-to-day%20work%20of%20a%20first-year%20analyst%20look%20like%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFC%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20My%20tasks%20are%20very%20diverse.%20I%20have%20my%20own%20long-term%20projects%20that%20could%20be%2C%20for%20example%2C%20implementing%20some%20new%20changes%2C%20visualizing%20something%20for%20my%20team%2C%20or%20building%20a%20dashboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20things%20could%20be%20fixing%20and%20improving%20our%20code%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20fun%20and%20academic%20tasks%2C%20for%20example%2C%20researching%2C%20looking%20at%20a%20paper%2C%20a%20specific%20model%2C%20a%20particular%20asset%20class%2C%20and%20explaining%20the%20returns.%20I'll%20write%20code%2C%20present%20the%20results%20to%20my%20team%2C%20and%20explain%20models%20and%20interesting%20patterns%20I%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20other%20analysts%20present%20a%20project%20for%20their%20manager%2C%20we'll%20look%20together%20at%20the%20risk%2C%20evaluate%20it%20based%20on%20the%20historical%20simulation%2C%20and%20how%20we%20can%20restructure%20our%20portfolio%20to%20try%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20particular%20situation%20or%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20a%20particular%20catalyst.%20I%20also%20listen%20in%20when%20we%20have%20experts%20and%20consultants%20come%20to%20speak%20%E2%80%94%20learning%20what%20they%20say%20about%20specific%20events%20or%20a%20specific%20economic%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20trade%2C%20I%20help%20with%20reporting%20the%20trades%2C%20keeping%20track%20of%20them%2C%20and%20interfacing%20with%20the%20middle%20office%20for%20booking.%20I'm%20exposed%20to%20all%20the%20different%20parts%20of%20what%20my%20team%20does.%20And%20that%20provides%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20organic%20learning%2C%20which%20I'm%20sure%20will%20be%20helpful%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20When%20reflecting%20on%20year%20one%2C%20going%20from%20student%20and%20intern%20to%20full-time%20analyst%2C%20what%20has%20been%20unexpected%20for%20you%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFC%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20How%20much%20BAM%20invests%20in%20technology.%20I%20think%20that's%20something%20I%20was%20really%20impressed%20by%2C%20even%20when%20I%20was%20an%20intern.%20My%20internship%20was%20a%20few%20months%20before%20all%20the%20hype%20about%20LLMs%20and%20AI%2C%20and%20we%20already%20had%20our%20own%20implementation%20of%20LLMs.%20Seeing%20the%20evolution%20over%20time%2C%20and%20the%20tools%20that%20we%20have%20access%20to%20now%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20incredible%20because%20it%20effectively%20means%20the%20amount%20of%20work%20you%20can%20do%20is%20multiplied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20aspect%20is%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20learning%2C%20I%20can%20total