t%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20facing%20rejection%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20sales%20you%20could%20face%20rejection%20day-in%20and%20day-out%20for%20three%20weeks%20in%20a%20row.%20Even%20if%20you're%20the%20best%20salesperson%20in%20the%20world%2C%20you%20are%20bound%20to%20have%20weeks%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20how%20sales%20is.%20It's%20an%20emotional%20roller%20coaster.%20I%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20Gen%20Z%20salespeople%20quit%20when%20they're%20in%20that%20low%20period%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20missing%20out%20on%20an%20opportunity%20to%20make%20probably%20triple%20what%20they%20were%20making%20if%20they%20were%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20role%20and%20give%20it%20another%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20think%20the%20fear%20of%20rejection%20over%20and%20over%20again%20is%20probably%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20that%20they%20face.%20These%20are%20my%20suggestions%20for%20overcoming%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227735d018-5bac-4cd9-97f7-f1bffb876f2b%5C%22%3EHave%20a%20routine%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fdoomscrolling%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejust%20sitting%2C%20doomscrolling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%20%26quot%3Bhow%20am%20I%20going%20to%20get%20back%20into%20the%20right%20mindset%20of%20doing%20really%20well%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20have%20these%20moments%2C%20I%20try%20to%20stick%20to%20a%20routine%20and%20a%20structure.%20For%20me%2C%20that's%20my%20morning%20workout%20and%20making%20coffee%20at%20home%20or%20going%20to%20get%20a%20coffee.%20That%20gets%20me%20out%20of%20bed%20and%20automatically%20makes%20me%20feel%20like%20the%20daunting%20tasks%20that%20I%20had%20when%20I%20first%20woke%20up%20aren't%20as%20daunting%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20recommend%20finding%20a%20really%20good%20morning%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0a3ad97-6a71-45cb-a621-b5aeb5