20rice%20processing%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20farmers%2C%20the%20real%20challenge%20begins%20not%20in%20the%20fields%20but%20at%20the%20mills%20where%20paddy%20is%20converted%20into%20market-ready%20rice.%20Traditional%20diesel-powered%20mills%20dominate%20villages%20across%20India%2C%20but%20they%20are%20unsuitable%20for%20small-scale%20operations.%20Recovery%20rates%20are%20low%2C%20often%20yielding%20less%20than%20300%20kg%20of%20rice%20from%20every%20500%20kg%20of%20paddy%20processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20is%20severe%20as%20farmers%20lose%20volume%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277246%2Fbankers-turn-farmers-organic-farming-middlemen-profits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20grain%20quality%20suffers%2C%20and%20profits%20fall%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20little%20control%20over%20the%20process%2C%20many%20end%20up%20selling%20raw%20paddy%20at%20throwaway%20prices%2C%20sacrificing%20both%20income%20and%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-25T132454.755_11zon-1756108543.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20are%20helping%20farmers%20process%20fresh%20rice%20as%20per%20the%20demands%20of%20their%20customers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-25T132454.755_11zon-1756108543.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-25T132454.755_11zon-1756108543-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Mod