ative%2C%20a%20collaboration%20between%20CEEW%20and%20Villgro%2C%20is%20helping%20innovations%20like%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20scale%20by%20providing%20enabling%20ecosystem%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInnovations%20like%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20often%20remain%20isolated%20if%20they%20do%20not%20connect%20with%20the%20right%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek.%20%E2%80%9COur%20role%20is%20to%20create%20those%20connections%2C%20making%20sure%20these%20technologies%20reach%20the%20farmers%20who%20need%20them%20most%2C%20backed%20by%20appropriate%20finance%2C%20supportive%20policy%2C%20and%20local%20demonstration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bridge%20the%20awareness%20gap%20and%20build%20confidence%20in%20the%20farmers%2C%20the%20programme%20facilitates%20demo%3Cbr%3Echampions%20and%20shows%20the%20value%20of%20technologies%20in%20action.%20The%20Powering%20Livelihoods%20programme%3Cbr%3Ealso%20works%20towards%20enabling%20end-user%20financing%20options%20for%20farmers%20who%20lack%20collateral%2C%20through%20partnerships%20with%20financiers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20programme%20team%20work%20closely%20with%20financial%20institutions%20to%20introduce%3Cbr%3Emechanisms%20like%20First%20Loss%20Default%20Guarantees.%20These%20tools%20reduce%20the%20risk%20lenders%20face%2C%20making%20it%3Cbr%3Eeasier%20for%20farmers%20with%20limited%20assets%20to%20access%20credit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20finance%2C%20Powering%20Livelihoods%20also%20pushes%20for%20policy%20convergence.%20The%20programme%20is%3Cbr%3Eworking%20towards%20the%20inclusion%20of%20renewable-powered%20processing%20equipment%20in%20national%20programmes%3Cbr%3Esuch%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Formalisation%20of%20Micro%20Food%20Processing%20Enterprises%20(PM-FME)%20scheme.%20This%3Cbr%3Ecan%20open%20access%20to%20credit-linked%20subsidies%20for%20farmers%20and%20microentrepreneurs%2C%20making%20adoption%3Cbr%3Emore%20affordable.%3